{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Many times"},{"time":2000,"text":"I go around the world to speak,"},{"time":5000,"text":"and people ask me questions"},{"time":7000,"text":"about the challenges,"},{"time":9000,"text":"my moments,"},{"time":12000,"text":"some of my regrets."},{"time":14000,"text":"1998:"},{"time":17000,"text":"A single mother of four,"},{"time":19000,"text":"three months after the birth of my fourth child,"},{"time":23000,"text":"I went to do a job"},{"time":26000,"text":"as a research assistant."},{"time":30000,"text":"I went to Northern Liberia."},{"time":33000,"text":"And as part of the work,"},{"time":36000,"text":"the village would give you lodgings."},{"time":39000,"text":"And they gave me lodging with a single mother"},{"time":42000,"text":"and her daughter."}]},{"cues":[{"time":44000,"text":"This girl happened to be"},{"time":47000,"text":"the only girl in the entire village"},{"time":49000,"text":"who had made it"},{"time":51000,"text":"to the ninth grade."},{"time":53000,"text":"She was the laughing stock of the community."},{"time":56000,"text":"Her mother was often told by other women,"},{"time":59000,"text":"\"You and your child"},{"time":61000,"text":"will die poor.\""},{"time":64000,"text":"After two weeks of working in that village,"},{"time":67000,"text":"it was time to go back."},{"time":69000,"text":"The mother came to me, knelt down,"},{"time":73000,"text":"and said, \"Leymah, take my daughter."},{"time":77000,"text":"I wish for her"},{"time":79000,"text":"to be a nurse.\""},{"time":82000,"text":"Dirt poor, living in the home with my parents,"},{"time":86000,"text":"I couldn't afford to."},{"time":89000,"text":"With tears in my eyes,"},{"time":91000,"text":"I said, \"No.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":94000,"text":"Two months later,"},{"time":96000,"text":"I go to another village"},{"time":98000,"text":"on the same assignment"},{"time":100000,"text":"and they asked me to live with the village chief."},{"time":104000,"text":"The women's chief of the village has this little girl,"},{"time":107000,"text":"fair color like me,"},{"time":109000,"text":"totally dirty."},{"time":111000,"text":"And all day she walked around"},{"time":113000,"text":"only in her underwear."},{"time":115000,"text":"When I asked, \"Who is that?\""},{"time":118000,"text":"She said, \"That's Wei."},{"time":120000,"text":"The meaning of her name is pig."},{"time":123000,"text":"Her mother died while giving birth to her,"},{"time":126000,"text":"and no one had any idea who her father was.\""},{"time":129000,"text":"For two weeks, she became my companion,"},{"time":132000,"text":"slept with me."},{"time":134000,"text":"I bought her used clothes"},{"time":136000,"text":"and bought her her first doll."},{"time":138000,"text":"The night before I left,"},{"time":141000,"text":"she came to the room"},{"time":143000,"text":"and said, \"Leymah, don't leave me here."},{"time":145000,"text":"I wish to go with you."},{"time":147000,"text":"I wish to go to school.\""},{"time":149000,"text":"Dirt poor, no money,"},{"time":152000,"text":"living with my parents,"},{"time":154000,"text":"I again said, \"No.\""},{"time":156000,"text":"Two months later,"},{"time":158000,"text":"both of those villages fell into another war."},{"time":161000,"text":"Till today, I have no idea"},{"time":165000,"text":"where those two girls are."}]},{"cues":[{"time":167000,"text":"Fast-forward, 2004:"},{"time":171000,"text":"In the peak of our activism,"},{"time":174000,"text":"the minister of Gender Liberia called me"},{"time":176000,"text":"and said, \"Leymah, I have a nine-year-old for you."},{"time":179000,"text":"I want you to bring her home"},{"time":181000,"text":"because we don't have safe homes.\""},{"time":183000,"text":"The story of this little girl:"},{"time":185000,"text":"She had been raped"},{"time":187000,"text":"by her paternal grandfather"},{"time":189000,"text":"every day for six months."},{"time":191000,"text":"She came to me bloated,"},{"time":194000,"text":"very pale."},{"time":196000,"text":"Every night I'd come from work and lie on the cold floor."},{"time":199000,"text":"She'd lie beside me"},{"time":201000,"text":"and say, \"Auntie, I wish to be well."},{"time":204000,"text":"I wish to go to school.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":207000,"text":"2010:"},{"time":209000,"text":"A young woman stands before President Sirleaf"},{"time":212000,"text":"and gives her testimony"},{"time":214000,"text":"of how she and her siblings live together,"},{"time":217000,"text":"their father and mother died during the war."},{"time":220000,"text":"She's 19; her dream is to go to college"},{"time":223000,"text":"to be able to support them."},{"time":225000,"text":"She's highly athletic."},{"time":227000,"text":"One of the things that happens"},{"time":229000,"text":"is that she applies for a scholarship."},{"time":231000,"text":"Full scholarship. She gets it."},{"time":233000,"text":"Her dream of going to school,"},{"time":235000,"text":"her wish of being educated,"},{"time":237000,"text":"is finally here."},{"time":239000,"text":"She goes to school on the first day."},{"time":242000,"text":"The director of sports"},{"time":244000,"text":"who's responsible for getting her into the program"},{"time":246000,"text":"asks her to come out of class."},{"time":248000,"text":"And for the next three years,"},{"time":250000,"text":"her fate will be"},{"time":252000,"text":"having sex with him every day,"},{"time":255000,"text":"as a favor for getting her in school."}]},{"cues":[{"time":258000,"text":"Globally, we have policies,"},{"time":262000,"text":"international instruments,"},{"time":264000,"text":"work leaders."},{"time":266000,"text":"Great people have made commitments --"},{"time":268000,"text":"we will protect our children"},{"time":271000,"text":"from want and from fear."},{"time":273000,"text":"The U.N. has the Convention on the Rights of the Child."},{"time":277000,"text":"Countries like America, we've heard things like No Child Left Behind."},{"time":281000,"text":"Other countries come with different things."},{"time":284000,"text":"There is a Millennium Development called Three"},{"time":286000,"text":"that focuses on girls."},{"time":290000,"text":"All of these great works by great people"},{"time":292000,"text":"aimed at getting young people"},{"time":294000,"text":"to where we want to get them globally,"},{"time":297000,"text":"I think, has failed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":299000,"text":"In Liberia, for example,"},{"time":302000,"text":"the teenage pregnancy rate"},{"time":304000,"text":"is three to every 10 girls."},{"time":308000,"text":"Teen prostitution is at its peak."},{"time":311000,"text":"In one community, we're told,"},{"time":313000,"text":"you wake up in the morning"},{"time":315000,"text":"and see used condoms like used chewing gum paper."},{"time":319000,"text":"Girls as young as 12 being prostituted"},{"time":322000,"text":"for less than a dollar a night."},{"time":326000,"text":"It's disheartening, it's sad."},{"time":329000,"text":"And then someone asked me,"},{"time":331000,"text":"just before my TEDTalk, a few days ago,"},{"time":333000,"text":"\"So where is the hope?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":335000,"text":"Several years ago, a few friends of mine"},{"time":338000,"text":"decided we needed to bridge the disconnect"},{"time":340000,"text":"between our generation"},{"time":342000,"text":"and the generation of young women."},{"time":344000,"text":"It's not enough to say"},{"time":346000,"text":"you have two Nobel laureates from the Republic of Liberia"},{"time":349000,"text":"when your girls' kids are totally out there"},{"time":352000,"text":"and no hope, or seemingly no hope."},{"time":355000,"text":"We created a space"},{"time":357000,"text":"called the Young Girls Transformative Project."},{"time":360000,"text":"We go into rural communities"},{"time":363000,"text":"and all we do, like has been done in this room,"},{"time":366000,"text":"is create the space."},{"time":369000,"text":"When these girls sit,"},{"time":371000,"text":"you unlock intelligence,"},{"time":374000,"text":"you unlock passion,"},{"time":377000,"text":"you unlock commitment,"},{"time":379000,"text":"you unlock focus,"},{"time":381000,"text":"you unlock great leaders."},{"time":383000,"text":"Today, we've worked with over 300."},{"time":386000,"text":"And some of those girls"},{"time":388000,"text":"who walked in the room very shy"},{"time":390000,"text":"have taken bold steps, as young mothers,"},{"time":393000,"text":"to go out there and advocate"},{"time":396000,"text":"for the rights of other young women."}]},{"cues":[{"time":399000,"text":"One young woman I met,"},{"time":401000,"text":"teen mother of four,"},{"time":403000,"text":"never thought about finishing high school,"},{"time":405000,"text":"graduated successfully;"},{"time":408000,"text":"never thought about going to college,"},{"time":410000,"text":"enrolled in college."},{"time":412000,"text":"One day she said to me,"},{"time":414000,"text":"\"My wish is to finish college"},{"time":416000,"text":"and be able to support my children.\""},{"time":418000,"text":"She's at a place where she can't find money"},{"time":420000,"text":"to go to school."},{"time":422000,"text":"She sells water, sells soft drinks"},{"time":425000,"text":"and sells recharge cards for cellphones."},{"time":429000,"text":"And you would think she would take that money"},{"time":431000,"text":"and put it back into her education."},{"time":434000,"text":"Juanita is her name."},{"time":436000,"text":"She takes that money"},{"time":438000,"text":"and finds single mothers in her community"},{"time":441000,"text":"to send back to school."},{"time":443000,"text":"Says, \"Leymah, my wish"},{"time":445000,"text":"is to be educated."},{"time":447000,"text":"And if I can't be educated,"},{"time":449000,"text":"when I see some of my sisters being educated,"},{"time":452000,"text":"my wish has been fulfilled."},{"time":454000,"text":"I wish for a better life."},{"time":456000,"text":"I wish for food for my children."},{"time":458000,"text":"I wish that sexual abuse and exploitation in schools would stop.\""},{"time":463000,"text":"This is the dream of the African girl."}]},{"cues":[{"time":465000,"text":"Several years ago,"},{"time":467000,"text":"there was one African girl."},{"time":469000,"text":"This girl had a son"},{"time":471000,"text":"who wished for a piece of doughnut"},{"time":474000,"text":"because he was extremely hungry."},{"time":477000,"text":"Angry, frustrated,"},{"time":480000,"text":"really upset"},{"time":482000,"text":"about the state of her society"},{"time":485000,"text":"and the state of her children,"},{"time":487000,"text":"this young girl started a movement,"},{"time":489000,"text":"a movement of ordinary women"},{"time":491000,"text":"banding together"},{"time":493000,"text":"to build peace."},{"time":495000,"text":"I will fulfill the wish."},{"time":497000,"text":"This is another African girl's wish."},{"time":499000,"text":"I failed to fulfill the wish of those two girls."},{"time":501000,"text":"I failed to do this."},{"time":503000,"text":"These were the things that were going through the head of this other young woman --"},{"time":506000,"text":"I failed, I failed, I failed."},{"time":509000,"text":"So I will do this."},{"time":513000,"text":"Women came out,"},{"time":515000,"text":"protested a brutal dictator,"},{"time":518000,"text":"fearlessly spoke."},{"time":521000,"text":"Not only did the wish of a piece of doughnut come true,"},{"time":525000,"text":"the wish of peace came true."},{"time":527000,"text":"This young woman"},{"time":529000,"text":"wished also to go to school."},{"time":531000,"text":"She went to school."},{"time":533000,"text":"This young woman wished for other things to happen,"},{"time":535000,"text":"it happened for her."}]},{"cues":[{"time":537000,"text":"Today, this young woman is me,"},{"time":541000,"text":"a Nobel laureate."},{"time":543000,"text":"I'm now on a journey"},{"time":545000,"text":"to fulfill the wish,"},{"time":547000,"text":"in my tiny capacity,"},{"time":549000,"text":"of little African girls --"},{"time":551000,"text":"the wish of being educated."},{"time":553000,"text":"We set up a foundation."},{"time":555000,"text":"We're giving full four-year scholarships"},{"time":557000,"text":"to girls from villages that we see with potential."}]},{"cues":[{"time":560000,"text":"I don't have much to ask of you."},{"time":563000,"text":"I've also been to places in this U.S.,"},{"time":565000,"text":"and I know that girls in this country"},{"time":567000,"text":"also have wishes,"},{"time":569000,"text":"a wish for a better life somewhere in the Bronx,"},{"time":572000,"text":"a wish for a better life"},{"time":574000,"text":"somewhere in downtown L.A.,"},{"time":576000,"text":"a wish for a better life somewhere in Texas,"},{"time":579000,"text":"a wish for a better life somewhere in New York,"},{"time":582000,"text":"a wish for a better life"},{"time":584000,"text":"somewhere in New Jersey."}]},{"cues":[{"time":586000,"text":"Will you journey with me"},{"time":588000,"text":"to help that girl,"},{"time":591000,"text":"be it an African girl or an American girl"},{"time":594000,"text":"or a Japanese girl,"},{"time":596000,"text":"fulfill her wish,"},{"time":598000,"text":"fulfill her dream,"},{"time":600000,"text":"achieve that dream?"},{"time":602000,"text":"Because all of these"},{"time":604000,"text":"great innovators and inventors"},{"time":607000,"text":"that we've talked to and seen"},{"time":609000,"text":"over the last few days"},{"time":611000,"text":"are also sitting in tiny corners"},{"time":614000,"text":"in different parts of the world,"},{"time":616000,"text":"and all they're asking us to do"},{"time":618000,"text":"is create that space"},{"time":620000,"text":"to unlock the intelligence,"},{"time":622000,"text":"unlock the passion,"},{"time":624000,"text":"unlock all of the great things"},{"time":626000,"text":"that they hold within themselves."},{"time":629000,"text":"Let's journey together. Let's journey together."}]},{"cues":[{"time":632000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":634000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":657000,"text":"Chris Anderson: Thank you so much."},{"time":659000,"text":"Right now in Liberia,"},{"time":661000,"text":"what do you see"},{"time":663000,"text":"as the main issue that troubles you?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":666000,"text":"LG: I've been asked to lead"},{"time":668000,"text":"the Liberian Reconciliation Initiative."},{"time":671000,"text":"As part of my work,"},{"time":673000,"text":"I'm doing these tours"},{"time":676000,"text":"in different villages and towns --"},{"time":678000,"text":"13, 15 hours on dirt roads --"},{"time":682000,"text":"and there is no community that I've gone into"},{"time":685000,"text":"that I haven't seen intelligent girls."},{"time":689000,"text":"But sadly,"},{"time":691000,"text":"the vision of a great future,"},{"time":694000,"text":"or the dream of a great future,"},{"time":696000,"text":"is just a dream,"},{"time":698000,"text":"because you have all of these vices."},{"time":700000,"text":"Teen pregnancy, like I said, is epidemic."}]},{"cues":[{"time":703000,"text":"So what troubles me"},{"time":705000,"text":"is that I was at that place"},{"time":709000,"text":"and somehow I'm at this place,"},{"time":712000,"text":"and I just don't want to be the only one"},{"time":714000,"text":"at this place."},{"time":716000,"text":"I'm looking for ways"},{"time":718000,"text":"for other girls to be with me."},{"time":720000,"text":"I want to look back 20 years from now"},{"time":723000,"text":"and see that there's another Liberian girl,"},{"time":725000,"text":"Ghanaian girl, Nigerian girl, Ethiopian girl"},{"time":728000,"text":"standing on this TED stage."},{"time":731000,"text":"And maybe, just maybe, saying,"},{"time":733000,"text":"\"Because of that Nobel laureate"},{"time":735000,"text":"I'm here today.\""},{"time":737000,"text":"So I'm troubled"},{"time":739000,"text":"when I see them like there's no hope."},{"time":742000,"text":"But I'm also not pessimistic,"},{"time":745000,"text":"because I know it doesn't take a lot"},{"time":747000,"text":"to get them charged up."}]},{"cues":[{"time":749000,"text":"CA: And in the last year,"},{"time":751000,"text":"tell us one hopeful thing"},{"time":753000,"text":"that you've seen happening."}]},{"cues":[{"time":755000,"text":"LG: I can tell you many hopeful things that I've seen happening."},{"time":758000,"text":"But in the last year,"},{"time":760000,"text":"where President Sirleaf comes from, her village,"},{"time":762000,"text":"we went there to work with these girls."},{"time":764000,"text":"And we could not find 25 girls"},{"time":766000,"text":"in high school."},{"time":768000,"text":"All of these girls went to the gold mine,"},{"time":771000,"text":"and they were predominantly prostitutes"},{"time":773000,"text":"doing other things."},{"time":775000,"text":"We took 50 of those girls"},{"time":777000,"text":"and we worked with them."},{"time":779000,"text":"And this was at the beginning of elections."},{"time":782000,"text":"This is one place where women were never --"},{"time":784000,"text":"even the older ones"},{"time":786000,"text":"barely sat in the circle with the men."},{"time":789000,"text":"These girls banded together and formed a group"},{"time":792000,"text":"and launched a campaign"},{"time":794000,"text":"for voter registration."},{"time":796000,"text":"This is a real rural village."},{"time":798000,"text":"And the theme they used was:"},{"time":800000,"text":"\"Even pretty girls vote.\""},{"time":802000,"text":"They were able to mobilize young women."}]},{"cues":[{"time":804000,"text":"But not only did they do that,"},{"time":807000,"text":"they went to those who were running for seats"},{"time":809000,"text":"to ask them, \"What is it"},{"time":811000,"text":"that you will give the girls of this community"},{"time":813000,"text":"when you win?\""},{"time":815000,"text":"And one of the guys"},{"time":817000,"text":"who already had a seat was very --"},{"time":820000,"text":"because Liberia has one of the strongest rape laws,"},{"time":822000,"text":"and he was one of those really fighting in parliament"},{"time":825000,"text":"to overturn that law"},{"time":827000,"text":"because he called it barbaric."},{"time":829000,"text":"Rape is not barbaric, but the law, he said, was barbaric."},{"time":833000,"text":"And when the girls started engaging him,"},{"time":835000,"text":"he was very hostile towards them."},{"time":837000,"text":"These little girls turned to him and said,"},{"time":839000,"text":"\"We will vote you out of office.\""},{"time":841000,"text":"He's out of office today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":843000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":849000,"text":"CA: Leymah, thank you. Thank you so much for coming to TED."}]},{"cues":[{"time":852000,"text":"LG: You're welcome. (CA: Thank you.)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":854000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}